snippet.title: Goat Simulator 3 - Gameplay Presentation - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description: Lightsabers, explosions and so much more appeared in the absurd, awesome Goat Simulator 3 trailer that debuted during the Future Games Show at Gamescom 2022. Goat Simulator 3 is coming to PC, Xbox Series X and S and PS5 on November 17.
